column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.modelMag_u-p.extinction_u,p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g-p.extinction_g,p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r-p.extinction_r,p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i-p.extinction_i,p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z-p.extinction_z,p.modelMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
